      <title>俄罗斯取消发射前一刻最新火箭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/russia-cancels-launch-of-newest-rocket-minute-before-lift-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在发射前大约一分钟取消了最新火箭的发射，且没有给出任何解释，使其陷入困境的太空计划遭遇挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/russia-cancels-launch-of-newest-rocket-minute-before-lift-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:22:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布兰森 5.2 亿美元的 Virgin Money 退出暴露了他的 SPAC 伤痕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/branson-s-520-million-virgin-money-exit-exposes-his-spac-scars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大约一年前，维珍集团(Virgin Group)创始人理查德·布兰森(Richard Branson)在全球股票市场上持有近20亿美元，其中大部分来自通过空白支票公司上市的几家烧钱的美国公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/branson-s-520-million-virgin-money-exit-exposes-his-spac-scars</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新兴股指有望创近两年来最高收盘价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/emerging-stock-index-heads-for-highest-close-in-nearly-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受一家亚洲芯片制造商股价飙升的推动，新兴市场股市周二上涨，并有望创下 2022 年 6 月以来的最佳收盘价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/emerging-stock-index-heads-for-highest-close-in-nearly-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:45:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉前首席执行官表示，马斯克可能推迟了低成本电动汽车计划，这令人遗憾</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/tesla-ex-ceo-says-shame-musk-may-have-delayed-low-cost-ev-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特斯拉公司前首席执行官马丁·艾伯哈德表示，该汽车制造商可能已经废弃了其廉价汽车，这是一种耻辱，因为降低电动汽车的价格是其普及的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/tesla-ex-ceo-says-shame-musk-may-have-delayed-low-cost-ev-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 07:09:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Atos 寻求 12 亿欧元的股权和债务用于救援计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/atos-seeks-1-2-billion-in-cash-and-loans-in-restructuring-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据向债权人提交的重组计划，陷入困境的法国 IT 公司 Atos SE 正在寻求 6 亿欧元（6.51 亿美元）现金以及另外 6 亿欧元信贷额度和贷款担保，为该业务提供资金到 2025 年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/atos-seeks-1-2-billion-in-cash-and-loans-in-restructuring-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能热潮带动韩国电力设备生产商股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/ai-boom-sends-korean-power-equipment-producers-shares-surging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受美国人工智能和数据中心电力需求预期激增的推动，韩国电气设备制造商的股票成为今年该国股市的最大赢家之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/ai-boom-sends-korean-power-equipment-producers-shares-surging</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 05:08:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
